# secretary-platform

Work in `secretary-platform/` unless editing repo-root Prettier config.

- Next.js **16** App Router — consult `node_modules/next/dist/docs/`; do not assume Next 14/15 APIs.
- `@/*` imports map to `src/*`.
- Stack: React 19, TypeScript strict, Tailwind v3.
- Run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` (in `secretary-platform/`) before finishing non-trivial changes.
- See `secretary-platform/CLAUDE.md` and `AGENTS.md` for commands and structure.
